items.name: Teleflora's Victorian Teacup Bouquet
items.description: Send warm wishes with this lovely gift bouquet that arrives in a ceramic teacup. This charming, old-fashioned bouquet features pink and crème roses.
items.arrangement: Cream roses, pink spray roses, miniature pink carnations and delicate pink limonium are presented in a teacup and saucer with a Victorian flower pattern.

items.name: Tempt Me Tulips Bouquet by Teleflora
items.description: Red hot! Whatever the occasion, these tempting tulips are sure to delight. The classic red blooms are gracefully arranged in a golden mercury glass vase for a touch of vintage romance.
items.arrangement: Includes ten red tulips. Delivered in a large Mercury Glass Julep.

items.name: Radiantly Red Tulips
items.description: Beautiful and "simply said" red tulips are a hip way to show you care.
items.arrangement: Ten romantic red Tulips arranged in a clear glass vase.

items.name: Teleflora's Sweet Surrender Bouquet
items.description: Surrender to the elegant, natural beauty of tulips. Over a dozen red and pink flowers are presented in our graceful Silver Reflections vase. It's an understated presentation that highlights the tulips' natural beauty - as well as your love and friendship.
items.arrangement: This gorgeous bouquet includes seven red tulips and eight pink tulips, delivered in our exclusive Silver Reflections vase, a metalized ceramic vase with a light pink tone.

items.name: Teleflora's It Had to Be You Bouquet
items.description: She's your one and only. Doesn't she deserve an equally singular bouquet? This charming, heartfelt arrangement puts a feminine spin on classic red roses by mixing in elegant red and pink tulips. Presented in our modern Mirrored Silver Cube, it's a uniquely stunning selection for any day you want to pamper your special one.
items.arrangement: This unique bouquet mixes large red roses and red spray roses with pink and red tulips. The flowers are delivered in our exclusive Mirrored Silver Cube vase.

items.name: Teleflora's Luminous Leaves Plant
items.description: Send your best wishes for a spectacular spring with this cheerful African violet plant, perfectly potted in a whimsical white glass vase with shimmering iridescent glaze.
items.arrangement: This gift features a living, potted African violet. Delivered in a Wonderful Whimsy cylinder.

items.name: Teleflora's Peaches and Dreams
items.description: The only thing sweeter than peaches and cream just might be this dreamy bouquet of delicious roses and tulips. Be a peach and send one today!
items.arrangement: Pretty in peach roses, tulips, miniature carnations and stock along with white waxflower and fresh spring greens are beautifully arranged in a ceramic French country container.

items.name: Teleflora's Sunny Kalanchoe
items.description: Bright and cheerful, this golden yellow kalanchoe plant in a keepsake, stained glass mosaic pot is a daily reminder of your gratitude!
items.arrangement: This joyful gift features a living, potted yellow kalanchoe plant. Delivered in a Blue Beauty Mosaic vase.

items.name: Zen Artistry
items.description: It's artistic arrangements like this one that make flowers such an integral and beautiful ingredient in feng shui. A brilliant green container and exotic palm leaf provide the perfect backdrop for purple orchids and a mix of delightful tropical flowers. This gift takes artistry to new heights.
items.arrangement: Purple dendrobium orchids, green carnations, dark pink Sweet William, an emerald palm leaf and other tropical greens are arranged in a square kiwi-colored container. Perfect when you've got a yen to send Zen!

items.name: Teleflora's Shades Of Brilliance Bouquet
items.description: Send her a rainbow! Golden lilies, radiant roses and regal alstroemeria burst brilliantly from a contemporary bamboo box. What a chic, stunning way to brighten her day!
items.arrangement: Gorgeous orange roses, yellow asiatic lilies, purple alstroemeria, hot pink carnations and green button spray chrysanthemums are arranged in a rainbow assortment with variegated aspidistra, lily grass and oregonia. Delivered in a Bamboo Rectangle vase.

items.name: Teleflora's Artistic Angles Bouquet
items.description: Celebrate with style! Presented in a mid-century ceramic planter with unique geometric motif, this artistic lily arrangement is one they'll never forget.
items.arrangement: A stunning gift from any angle! Add style to their celebration with this artistic lily arrangement, presented in a chic mid-century ceramic planter with sleek wood base.

items.name: Teleflora's Style Statement Bouquet
items.description: Gorgeous green blooms and a mod, mid-century ceramic planter add up to a stunning style statement!
items.arrangement: Green spider chrysanthemums, green button spray chrysanthemums, white sinuata statice, and blue eryngium are arranged with sword fern and variegated pittosporum. Delivered in a Mid Mod Geometric Planter.

items.name: Teleflora's Color Me Cute Bouquet
items.description: Cute, colorful and carefully curated, this artistic arrangement of hot pink lilies, orange roses and dramatic hala leaves is a tropically-inspired treat they'll adore!
items.arrangement: Orange roses, hot pink oriental lilies, orange carnations, miniature yellow carnations, and green cushion spray chrysanthemums are accented with hala leaf and lemon leaf. Delivered in a Leaf Color Splash cube.

items.name: Teleflora's Opulent Orchids
items.description: Pure elegance. That's what these divine white phalaenopsis orchids deliver. They're beautiful upon arrival, and what's even more beautiful is that these amazing plants are easy to take care of, and can blossom for months.
items.arrangement: A white phalaenopsis orchid plant arrives in an exclusive bamboo cube. Now that's the kind of opulence anyone can appreciate.

items.name: Teleflora's Garden Delights
items.description: Put a smile on her face and a spring in her step with this delightful little garden bouquet. Presented in a chic bamboo box, its happy hot pinks and lovely lime greens give a colorful pick-me-up!
items.arrangement: Bright pink roses and carnations are contrasted with green carnations and button spray chrysanthemums, light pink stock and delicate lavender waxflower -fresh greens include lemon leaves and soft dusty miller. Delivered in a sculptural natural bamboo vase to give it a contemporary look.

items.name: Now and Zen
items.description: Now and Zen you want to send something tall, and extra special. It's got to be unique, tropical and of course, beautiful. That is a tall order, but this arrangement handles it with panache!
items.arrangement: Gorgeous lavender cymbidium orchids, dark pink asiatic lilies, striking green anthuriums, leucadendron, ginger and more tropical lushness is hand-delivered in a contemporary box container. Wow!

items.name: Teleflora's Farmhouse Chic Bouquet
items.description: This country-inspired surprise is sure to brighten Mother's Day--or any day!--with its lush lavender blooms and chic stoneware pitcher with ombre glaze.
items.arrangement: Lavender roses, lavender stock, miniature pink carnations, raspberry sinuata statice and a potted echeveria succulent are arranged with parvifolia eucalyptus and huckleberry. Delivered in Teleflora's Farmhouse Chic Pitcher.

images.alt: Teleflora's Farmhouse Chic Bouquet Flower Arrangement
Teleflora's Farmhouse Chic Bouquet Flower Arrangement
Teleflora's Farmhouse Chic Bouquet Flower Arrangement

items.name: Teleflora's Secret Oasis
items.description: This lovely, serene bouquet makes a Zen-sational gift for any special occasion. They'll be thrilled with this artistic arrangement of orchids, lilies and exotic accents in a red bamboo dish. It's like a trip to Shangri-La.
items.arrangement: This exotic arrangement includes green dendrobium orchids, white asiatic lilies, an aralia leaf, green flax, bear grass, oregonia and mood moss accented with pieces of natural river cane. Delivered in a red bamboo dish.

items.name: Teleflora's Imperial Purple Orchid
items.description: Shangri-la might be a fictional place, but this stunning orchid is firmly planted in the most beautiful kind of reality. An exotic lavender phalaenopsis orchid comes delivered in a distinctive cube made of beautiful, natural bamboo. It's easy to take care of and lovely to look at.
items.arrangement: A lavender phalaenopsis orchid plant arrives in an exclusive bamboo cube. It's almost too good to be true.

items.name: Kissed With Bliss by Teleflora
items.description: An elegant way to show you care, this bit of bliss blends luxurious lavender roses with wondrous white lilies into a stunning floral sculpture. Accented with exotic greens and presented in a modern bamboo rectangular vase, it brings natural serenity to any space.
items.arrangement: Includes lavender roses, white asiatic lilies, lavender stock, monte cassino asters and green chrysanthemums, accented with fresh greenery. Delivered in a large Bamboo Rectangular vase.

vase.alt: Kissed With Bliss by Teleflora Vase

items.name: Regal Orchids
items.description: Grace. Beauty. Prosperity. And love. These are just some of the lovely qualities attached to the exquisite orchid. So imagine the effect of receiving six stunning orchid plants all at once. Magical, right?
items.arrangement: Two brilliant green miniature phalaenopsis orchids, two lavender miniature phalaenopsis orchids and two dazzling white miniature phalaenopsis orchids are surrounded by white river rocks and delivered in a unique crème ceramic pedestal planter. Give someone the royal treatment!

items.name: Teleflora's Grand Gesture
items.description: When you're inspired to make a grand gesture of any kind, this gorgeous tropical topiary is a natural choice. The calla lily symbolizes magnificent beauty and when mixed with graceful tropical leaves and arranged in a stunning bamboo dish, the results are extraordinary.
items.arrangement: White calla lilies, kale and tropical greens are delivered in a natural bamboo dish. Makes a grand gift!

items.name: Exquisite Beauty by Teleflora
items.description: No other name could possibly describe this exquisitely beautiful bouquet. Its brilliant blossoms are gorgeously arranged and delivered in an exclusive lavender vase. Let her know how special she is to you by sending this fabulous gift.
items.arrangement: Dazzling green hydrangea, hot pink and light pink roses, purple alstroemeria, mini carnations and statice, lavender freesia, pink heather and eucalyptus arrive in a lavender cube. Exquisitely exciting!

items.name: Teleflora's Ticket to Paradise
items.description: If a floral version of paradise is what you're after, this incredible gift is just the ticket. A masterful assortment of tropical flowers and greens is amazingly arranged in a distinctive rectangular natural bamboo container. Absolutely stunning.
items.arrangement: Lovely lavender hydrangea and roses, pink miniature callas, hot pink spray roses, purple carnations, heather, fern and more fill a natural bamboo container.
